	<h1>Leadership Team</h1>
	<details>
	<summary style="cursor: zoom-in;"><strong>Founder & CEO — Daniel Mercer</strong></summary>
	<p>Daniel Mercer founded Tactical Cyber after more than a decade working in IT operations and cybersecurity roles across both public and private sectors. His early career focused on network administration and infrastructure support, where he developed a strong appreciation for the operational realities that many security programs overlook.</p>
	<p>Over time, Mercer transitioned into security engineering and incident response, supporting organizations through ransomware events and large-scale system disruptions. These experiences shaped his belief that effective cybersecurity must be grounded in disciplined IT operations.</p>
	<p>As CEO, he continues to guide the company’s strategic direction, emphasizing sustainable security practices, client transparency, and long-term risk reduction.</p>
	</details>
